              Betty Pride</h1>
            <p id="9248:31881"
              class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-[20px] font-inter font-normal leading-6 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-[30px] text-left text-white w-full sm:w-4/5 lg:w-[60%]">
              Since 1983, Betty Pride has been at the heart of Nigeria's garment industry. From humble beginnings to
              becoming a trusted partner for schools, organizations, and fashion brands, our mission has remained the
              same: to deliver garments that combine quality, affordability, and reliability.</p>
          </div>

