              Our Story</h2>
            <p id="9248:31969"
              class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-[20px] font-inter font-normal leading-6 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-[30px] text-center text-[#000408] w-full">
              Founded in Lagos, Betty Pride grew from a small textile outfit into one of Nigeria's most reliable garment
              manufacturers. Over the past four decades, we've supplied uniforms for schools nationwide, produced
              corporate wear for some of the country's largest enterprises, and expanded into kids wear and fashion
              labels.</p>
          </div>

